data.description:
Welcome to your dream home! This Highland-built home in Clements Ranch offers comfort, functionality, and high-end upgrades. With 4 bedrooms, 3 bathrooms, and a game room, it's perfect for entertaining. The gourmet kitchen features stainless steel appliances and granite countertops. The master suite provides a relaxing retreat with a luxurious soaking tub and shower. Enjoy the privacy of the green belt and nearby amenities like walking trails, pool, and playground. Don't miss out on this extraordinary Highland home, your slice of paradise!

Everyone 18 and over must have an application. PLEASE DON'T DISTURB PROPERTY OWNERS. Lease is for one year only. Pets are on a case-by-case basis, please include picture of pet(s).$50.00 application fee.
